strings: <voice_0x0100121D><se_high>Accuracy: It seems you have ignored my advice to build a strong defense.
<voice_0x0100121E><se_def>daffodil: X is closed! You will never forgive me! I won't let you see Domenico!
<voice_0x0100121F><se_high>Accuracy: ...from Dominican Republic? ah ah ah ah ah ah
<voice_0x01001221><se_high>Accuracy: sorry i dont know where he came from when he died...
<voice_0x01001222><se_high>Accuracy: I quickly realized that a great show and a grand palace are not the same.
<voice_0x01001223><se_high>Accuracy: I do not understand. I'm looking for the chosen descendant of the Greater Grail, one of the seven that sealed the Demon King's spike...
<voice_0x01001225><se_high>Accuracy: Unfortunately, the person who was supposed to protect her was not aware of his responsibility!
<voice_0x01001226><se_high>Accuracy: hey hey! I wonder when you'll come.
<voice_0x01001227><se_high>Accuracy: At that time! I know that at some point in the process I will have to fight you.
<voice_0x01001228><se_high>Accuracy: I confess that I was a little sad to see you die.
